description:
Create lib/permissions/matrix.ts with TypeScript config defining all permissions for each role (unauth/guest/member/admin). This becomes the single source of truth consumed by:
- Permission-checking functions
- Help page generation

Structure:
```typescript
export const PERMISSIONS = {
  issues: {
    report: { unauth: true, guest: true, member: true, admin: true },
    updateStatus: { unauth: false, guest: 'own', member: true, admin: true },
    updatePriority: { unauth: false, guest: false, member: true, admin: true },
    // ...
  },
  // ...
} as const;
```
